NOTE ON DEPENDENCIES

MifBridge is an editor-only Unreal Engine plugin. It links against Unreal
Engine headers/modules at build time; the Unreal Engine itself is governed by
the Epic Games Unreal Engine EULA, not this MIT license. This license covers
only the MifBridge plugin source in this repository.

MifBridge does not include, link, or redistribute any GPL-licensed code. The
`create_editable_child` endpoint calls an engine-side function
(`CreateEditableBlueprintCopy`, declared in the Kismet module of a
cooked-editor engine fork) and, at runtime only, cooperates with the separate
MifKismetReconstructor plugin (GPL-3.0) through an engine-provided delegate.
Those are distributed separately and are not part of this MIT work.
